ve plan also as announced on  january mr rochussen purchased a beneficial interest in one million ordinary shares which are held in the name of amigona holdings inc enquiries polar capital holdings plc gavin rochussen ceo john mansell coo     canaccord genuity  nomad and joint broker simon bridges  qe andrew buchanan       peel hunt  joint broker guy wiehahn     camarco  pr advisers ed gascoignepees           disclosure as required in accordance with schedule  of the aim rules for companies full name gavin mark rochussen age  previous names none directorships a full list of gavin rochussens current directorships and past directorships held within the last five years were provided in the announcement on  january  rns u  an updated list is provided below  current directorships as at  july  position company independent partnership advisor james hambro  partners llp governor and director tonbridge school advisor the gani iom trust and amigona holdings inc past directorships in the last five years position company chief executive j o hambro capital management limited president and director johcm usa inc executive director  international j o hambro capital management holdings limited director btim uk limited director johcm singapore pte partner representative james hambro  partners llp   apart from the disclosures above there are no further disclosures required to be made in respect of the appointment under schedule g or rule  of the aim rules for companies         this information is provided by rnsthe company news service from the london stock exchange  end  boaeakxlfflxeff quick links equity home equity prices and performance latest announcements our product portfolio wwwtrustnetcom wwwtrustnetoffshorecom wwwtrustnetmiddleeastcom   wwwinvestegatecouk wwwfundlistingscom fe analytics   data feeds factsheet and literature production webtools data provided by fe care has been taken to ensure that the information is correct but fe neither warrants represents nor guarantees 